title: The Inspector Wexford Crime Collection - Ruth Rendell
description:
Audio Books : Mystery and Suspense : Other quality : English


All are unabridged and are of CD quality . Most were collected and ripped by peterg23.
All are recorded at 48 kbps / 44 kHz Mono Fhg CBR MP3.
(All the narrators here are good. Half of the titles are read by Nigel Anthony - my personal favorite).



I previously made this superb series available here as a set in 2011. Here it is again as requested, but this time I've added the final book #24.

#1. From Doon with Death [1964], 5 hours 28 mins, read by Terrence Hardiman.


#2. A New Lease of Death [1967], 6 hours 53 mins, read by Nigel Anthony


#3. Wolf to the Slaughter [1967], 5 hours 56 mins, read by Robin Bailey


#4. The Best Man to Die [1969] , 6 hours 5 mins , read by Robin Bailey


#5. A Guilty Thing Surprised [1970], 5 hours 30 mins, read by Christopher Ravenscroft
The discovery of Elizabeth Nightingale's broken body in the woods near her home of the Nightingales' lives lie undercurrents and secrets no one ever suspected.
